Package de.hdm_stuttgart.mi.se1

Class TestMathOperationMethods

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hdm_stuttgart.mi.se1.TestMathOperationMethods

  • public class TestMathOperationMethods
extends java.lang.Object
    Unit tests for all possible math operations that can be used in the program. Using testHelper to simulate the process of the App.class and then check if the result fits. Only tests valuable entries, exceptions are tested in TestException.class.
